description	"Clone Jet Trooper

^2Weapons:
- DC-15A Blaster Rifle (1)
- EMP Launcher (1)
-- Ignores Blaster Defense
-- 100% More DMG
-- Pulse Stuns On Hit
-- Explosive Rounds
-- 75% Less Velocity
-- 15% Slower Movement
-- Mag Reload

^8Attributes:
- Fuel (3)
- 1 Reinforcement
- Assemble

Clone troopers were identical, genetically-modified soldiers bred and trained to serve in the Republic's army during the Clone Wars. This particular clone trooper is a standard clone trooper of the private rank, and make up the bulk of the clone army. The jet troopers carry an EMP launcher as well as a standard DC-15A blaster rifle."